#: capshipping/templates/about.html:82
msgid ""
"We offer reliable air and sea freight solutions with secure handling, fast "
"delivery, and trusted logistics services between the USA, Haiti, and the "
"Dominican Republic."
msgstr ""
"Nou ofri sèvis transpò pa avyon ak pa bato ki fyab, avèk sekirite nan "
"tretman pakè yo, livrezon rapid, ak sèvis lojistik ou ka fè konfyans ant "
"Etazini, Ayiti ak Repiblik Dominikèn."

