#: capshipping/templates/index.html:122
msgid "Receive Packages"
msgstr "Resevwa Pakè yo"

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:127
msgid ""
"Shop from your favorite stores in the United States and send your packages "
"directly to our warehouse..."
