#: capshipping/templates/index.html:387
msgid ""
"Cap Shipping Distribution is dedicated to providing fast, secure, and "
"reliable shipping solutions between the USA, Haiti, and the Dominican "
"Republic. Our mission is to simplify international shipping through trusted "
"customer service, efficient logistics, and affordable delivery options by "
"air and sea."
msgstr ""
"Cap Shipping Distribution angaje li pou bay solisyon ekspedisyon rapid, "
"sekirize ak fyab ant Etazini, Ayiti ak Repiblik Dominikèn. Misyon nou se "
"senplifye transpò entènasyonal atravè yon sèvis kliyan ou ka fè konfyans, "
"lojistik efikas, ak opsyon livrezon abòdab pa avyon ak pa bato."

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:394
msgid ""
"Our vision is to become one of the most trusted Caribbean logistics and "
"freight forwarding companies by connecting families and businesses through "
"innovative, secure, and professional shipping services worldwide."
msgstr ""
"Vizyon nou se vin youn nan konpayi lojistik ak transpò machandiz ki plis fè "
"konfyans nan Karayib la, lè nou konekte fanmi ak biznis atravè sèvis "
"ekspedisyon inovatè, sekirize ak pwofesyonèl atravè lemond."

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:402
msgid ""
"Cap Shipping Distribution was created with the goal of making international "
"shipping easier, faster, and more accessible for the Haitian and Caribbean "
"communities. Through dedication, transparency, and customer-focused service, "
"we continue to build a reliable logistics network customers can trust every "
"day."
msgstr ""
"Cap Shipping Distribution te kreye avèk objektif pou rann transpò "
"entènasyonal pi fasil, pi rapid ak pi aksesib pou kominote ayisyen ak "
"karayibeyen yo. Gras ak devouman, transparans ak sèvis ki santre sou kliyan "
"yo, nou kontinye bati yon rezo lojistik ki fyab kliyan yo ka fè konfyans "
"chak jou."

