#: capshipping/templates/index.html:624 capshipping/templates/tracking.html:318
msgid "How long does shipping from the USA to Haiti take?"
msgstr "Konbyen tan transpò soti Ozetazini pou rive Ayiti pran?"

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:630 capshipping/templates/tracking.html:324
msgid ""
"Delivery times depend on the shipping method you choose. Air freight is "
"faster for urgent packages, while sea freight is more affordable for larger "
"shipments. Our team always works to ensure safe and on-time delivery."
msgstr ""
"Tan livrezon an depann de kalite transpò ou chwazi a. Transpò pa avyon pi "
"rapid pou pakè ijan, pandan transpò pa bato pi abòdab pou gwo chajman yo. "
"Ekip nou an toujou travay pou asire livrezon yo fèt an sekirite epi alè."

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:642 capshipping/templates/tracking.html:336
msgid "Can I track my package in real time?"
msgstr "Èske mwen ka swiv pakè mwen an an tan reyèl?"

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:650 capshipping/templates/tracking.html:344
msgid ""
"Yes, we provide real-time package tracking so you can follow your shipment "
"from our warehouse in the USA until it arrives at its final destination."
msgstr ""
"Wi, nou bay sèvis swiv pakè an tan reyèl pou ou ka suiv ekspedisyon ou depi "
"nan depo nou Ozetazini jouk li rive nan destinasyon final li."

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:662 capshipping/templates/tracking.html:356
msgid "What items are allowed for shipping?"
msgstr "Ki atik ki otorize pou ekspedisyon?"

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:670 capshipping/templates/tracking.html:364
msgid ""
"We ship clothing, electronics, household items, business goods, and many "
"other products. However, restricted or prohibited items cannot be accepted "
"for transportation."
msgstr ""
"Nou ekspedye rad, aparèy elektwonik, atik pou kay, machandiz komèsyal ak "
"anpil lòt pwodwi ankò. Sepandan, atik ki entèdi oswa ki gen restriksyon pa "
"kapab aksepte pou transpò."

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:684 capshipping/templates/tracking.html:378
msgid "Do you offer both air and sea cargo services?"
msgstr "Èske nou ofri sèvis kago pa avyon ak pa bato? "

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:692 capshipping/templates/tracking.html:386
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    Yes, we offer both fast air cargo and cost-effective sea "
"freight services to give customers flexible shipping solutions based on "
"their needs and budget.\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"Wi, nou ofri sèvis kago pa avyon ki rapid ansanm ak sèvis transpò pa bato ki "
"pi ekonomik, pou bay kliyan yo solisyon livrezon fleksib selon bezwen ak "
"bidjè yo. "

