#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:106
msgid "1. Introduction"
msgstr "1. Entwodiksyon"

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:109
msgid ""
"These Terms & Conditions govern your use of our shipping services and "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Tèm ak Kondisyon sa yo gouvène itilizasyon sèvis ekspedisyon nou yo ansanm "
"ak sit entènèt nou an."

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:124
msgid ""
"\n"
"    By using Cap Shipping Distribution LLC services, you agree to comply "
"with our shipping policies, operational procedures, and delivery terms. We "
"provide freight forwarding, package handling, and logistics solutions "
"between the United States, Haiti, and the Dominican Republic. Customers are "
"responsible for providing accurate shipment information, including recipient "
"details, package contents, and contact information. Any false, prohibited, "
"or incomplete information may result in shipment delays, refusal, or "
"additional charges. Our team is committed to ensuring safe handling, timely "
"transportation, and reliable customer support throughout the shipping "
"process.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"Lè ou itilize sèvis Cap Shipping Distribution LLC yo, ou dakò respekte "
"politik ekspedisyon nou yo, pwosedi operasyonèl nou yo ak kondisyon livrezon "
"yo. Nou bay sèvis transpò machandiz, tretman pakè ak solisyon lojistik ant "
"Etazini, Ayiti ak Repiblik Dominikèn. Kliyan yo responsab pou bay enfòmasyon "
"ki egzak sou ekspedisyon yo, tankou detay moun k ap resevwa a, sa ki nan "
"pakè yo ak enfòmasyon kontak yo. Nenpòt enfòmasyon ki fo, entèdi oswa ki pa "
"konplè kapab lakòz reta, refi oswa frè adisyonèl sou ekspedisyon an. Ekip "
"nou an angaje li pou asire tretman an fèt an sekirite, transpò fèt alè ak "
"sipò kliyan ki fyab pandan tout pwosesis ekspedisyon an."

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:152
msgid ""
"\n"
"    Cap Shipping Distribution LLC provides air and sea freight services for "
"packages, personal items, commercial goods, and cargo between the United "
"States, Haiti, and the Dominican Republic. Our services include shipment "
"collection, package consolidation, warehouse handling, transportation, "
"tracking updates, and delivery support. Delivery times may vary depending on "
"the shipping method, customs clearance, weather conditions, and destination "
"location.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"Cap Shipping Distribution LLC bay sèvis transpò pa avyon ak pa bato pou "
"pakè, atik pèsonèl, machandiz komèsyal ak kago ant Etazini, Ayiti ak "
"Repiblik Dominikèn. Sèvis nou yo gen ladan ranmasaj ekspedisyon yo, gwoupman "
"pakè yo, tretman nan depo, transpò, mizajou sou suiv pakè yo ak sipò pou "
"livrezon yo. Tan livrezon yo ka varye selon kalite transpò a, pwosedi ladwàn "
"yo, kondisyon metewolojik yo ak kote destinasyon an ye."

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:194
msgid "3. User Responsibilities"
msgstr "3. Responsablite Itilizatè yo"

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:197
msgid ""
"\n"
"    Customers are responsible for providing accurate shipping information, "
"including names, addresses, phone numbers, and package descriptions. All "
"items must be properly packaged to ensure safe transportation. Customers "
"must also comply with all shipping regulations and avoid sending prohibited, "
"illegal, dangerous, or restricted items. Cap Shipping Distribution LLC is "
"not responsible for delays, losses, or additional fees caused by incorrect "
"information or improper packaging provided by the customer.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"Kliyan yo responsab pou bay enfòmasyon ekspedisyon ki egzak, tankou non, "
"adrès, nimewo telefòn ak deskripsyon pakè yo. Tout atik yo dwe byen anbale "
"pou asire transpò yo fèt an sekirite. Kliyan yo dwe respekte tout règleman "
"transpò yo epi evite voye atik ki entèdi, ilegal, danjere oswa ki gen "
"restriksyon. Cap Shipping Distribution LLC pa responsab pou reta, pèt oswa "
"frè adisyonèl ki koze pa move enfòmasyon oswa move anbalaj kliyan an bay."

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:214
msgid ""
"\n"
"    We are committed to providing secure, reliable, and professional "
"shipping services while ensuring transparency, customer satisfaction, and "
"smooth logistics operations for every shipment entrusted to our company.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"Nou angaje nou pou bay sèvis ekspedisyon ki sekirize, fyab ak pwofesyonèl, "
"pandan nou asire transparans, satisfaksyon kliyan yo ak bon fonksyònman "
"operasyon lojistik yo pou chak ekspedisyon yo konfye konpayi nou an."

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:239
msgid "4. Delivery Time"
msgstr "4. Tan Livrezon"

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:242
msgid ""
"\n"
"    Delivery times provided by Cap Shipping Distribution LLC are estimated "
"and may vary depending on customs inspections, weather conditions, "
"transportation delays, holidays, or other circumstances beyond our control. "
"While we work to ensure timely deliveries, we cannot guarantee exact "
"delivery dates. The company is not responsible for damages, losses, or "
"delays caused by customs authorities, natural events, accidents, or improper "
"packaging by the customer. Customers are encouraged to securely package "
"fragile or valuable items before shipment.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"Tan livrezon Cap Shipping Distribution LLC bay yo se estimasyon sèlman epi "
"yo ka varye selon enspeksyon ladwàn, kondisyon metewolojik, reta transpò, "
"jou ferye oswa lòt sitiyasyon ki depase kontwòl nou. Menmsi nou travay pou "
"asire livrezon yo fèt alè, nou pa kapab garanti dat livrezon egzak yo. "
"Konpayi an pa responsab pou domaj, pèt oswa reta ki koze pa otorite ladwàn "
"yo, evènman natirèl, aksidan oswa move anbalaj kliyan an fè. Nou ankouraje "
"kliyan yo pou byen anbale atik frajil oswa ki gen anpil valè anvan "
"ekspedisyon an."

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:259
msgid ""
"\n"
"    We continuously strive to provide reliable shipping services and clear "
"communication to ensure every customer receives the best possible logistics "
"experience with transparency and professionalism.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"Nou kontinye fè tout efò pou bay sèvis ekspedisyon ki fyab ansanm ak "
"kominikasyon ki klè pou asire chak kliyan jwenn pi bon eksperyans lojistik "
"posib avèk transparans ak pwofesyonalis."

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:284
msgid "5. Payments & Fees"
msgstr "5. Peman ak Frè yo"

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:287
msgid ""
"\n"
"    All shipping fees, service charges, customs costs, storage fees, and "
"other applicable charges must be fully paid before shipment processing or "
"delivery. Prices may vary depending on package size, weight, destination, "
"shipping method, and additional services requested. Cap Shipping "
"Distribution LLC reserves the right to refuse shipment release or delivery "
"until all outstanding balances are cleared. Additional fees may also apply "
"for oversized packages, restricted items, returned shipments, or extended "
"warehouse storage.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"Tout frè ekspedisyon, frè sèvis, depans ladwàn, frè depo ak lòt frè ki "
"aplikab yo dwe peye nèt anvan tretman oswa livrezon ekspedisyon an fèt. Pri "
"yo ka varye selon gwosè pakè a, pwa li, destinasyon an, kalite transpò a ak "
"sèvis adisyonèl kliyan an mande yo. Cap Shipping Distribution LLC rezève dwa "
"pou refize remèt oswa livre yon ekspedisyon toutotan tout balans ki poko "
"peye yo pa regle. Frè adisyonèl kapab aplike tou pou gwo pakè, atik ki gen "
"restriksyon, ekspedisyon retounen oswa depo ki dire twò lontan."

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:304
msgid ""
"\n"
"    Customers are encouraged to review all pricing details and payment "
"conditions carefully before confirming any shipment or logistics service "
"with our company.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"Nou ankouraje kliyan yo pou verifye tout detay sou pri yo ansanm ak "
"kondisyon peman yo avèk anpil atansyon anvan yo konfime nenpòt ekspedisyon "
"oswa sèvis lojistik ak konpayi nou an."

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:329
msgid "6. Prohibited Items"
msgstr "6. Atik Entèdi yo"

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:332
msgid ""
"\n"
"    Customers are strictly prohibited from shipping illegal, hazardous, "
"flammable, explosive, counterfeit, or restricted items through Cap Shipping "
"Distribution LLC services. This includes weapons, drugs, toxic materials, "
"and any products prohibited by local or international shipping regulations. "
"The company reserves the right to inspect, refuse, hold, or report "
"suspicious shipments to the appropriate authorities when necessary. Any "
"violation of these policies may result in shipment cancellation, legal "
"action, fines, or permanent suspension of service access.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"Kliyan yo entèdi nèt pou ekspedye atik ilegal, danjere, ki pran dife fasil, "
"eksplozif, fo pwodwi oswa atik ki gen restriksyon atravè sèvis Cap Shipping "
"Distribution LLC yo. Sa gen ladan zam, dwòg, materyèl toksik ak nenpòt "
"pwodwi règleman transpò lokal oswa entènasyonal entèdi. Konpayi an rezève "
"dwa pou enspekte, refize, kenbe oswa rapòte nenpòt ekspedisyon sispèk bay "
"otorite ki konsène yo lè sa nesesè. Nenpòt vyolasyon règleman sa yo kapab "
"lakòz anilasyon ekspedisyon an, aksyon legal, amann oswa sispansyon pèmanan "
"aksè ak sèvis yo."

#: capshipping/templates/term_and_condition.html:349
msgid ""
"\n"
"    Our priority is to maintain safe, secure, and compliant shipping "
"operations while protecting customers, employees, and transportation "
"partners throughout the delivery process.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"Priyorite nou se kenbe operasyon ekspedisyon yo an sekirite, byen pwoteje "
"epi an konfòmite ak règleman yo, pandan n ap pwoteje kliyan yo, anplwaye yo "
"ak patnè transpò yo pandan tout pwosesis livrezon an."

